                                        <li><strong>Volume Buttons:</strong> Press the UP volume button several times</li>
                                        <li><strong>Control Center:</strong> Swipe down from top-right, ensure media volume is high</li>
                                        <li><strong>Test Audio:</strong> Click "Test Audio Playback" above</li>
                                        <li><strong>Listen Page:</strong> Always tap "?? Enable iPhone Audio" button when listening</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
